articles.title: Football transfer rumours: Barcelona to reject Sancho swap; Real Madrid eye shock Tielemans move - 90min UK
articles.description: Tuesday's transfer rumour roundup includes news on Barcelona's dismissing Man Utd's Jadon Sancho swap proposal, Real Madrid's interest in Youri Tielemans and more.
articles.content:
90min rounds up the latest transfer news, rumours and gossip circulating around the world...
Barcelona will not entertain any attempt by Manchester United to try and swap Jadon Sancho for Raphinha. … [+2060 chars]
